{"tid":808294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[眾人皆醉] 湯家驊:奇怪港府外無人覺陳浩天出賣香港","createTime":"2018-09-06T08:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T17:48:07.000Z","uid":77196,"like":146,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"8ebefddb8ac7b77e955ce310f117384faa5fdd0e","tid":808294,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:25:45.000Z","msg":"香港民族黨召集人陳浩天上周六再次去信美國華府，呼籲美國國務院取消《香港政策法》。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊昨日在facebook發文，指陳浩天為何對特區政府充滿憤怒和仇恨，誓要置特區於死地，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但奇怪的是，除了特區政府外，似乎沒有人覺得他的行為不妥，更沒有人說他出賣香港</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中大學生會會長區倬僖日前在開學禮致詞時提及港獨，湯家驊則指年青人以身試法，猶如盲人玩火，後果難料；更何況到了今天，應該知道在「一國兩制」下，民主不是可以逼出來的。"},{"pid":"34bbec1b58923145486c2a7116dfe74871955904","tid":808294,"uid":20816,"like":217,"dislike":3,"score":214,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:29:55.000Z","msg":"因為我們沒有「衰十一」"},{"pid":"45ca0dcd394698d800e502a0a15c7c321c944d37","tid":808294,"uid":202464,"like":133,"dislike":2,"score":131,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:31:31.000Z","msg":"因為我地無人有痛腳畀支那渣手"},{"pid":"1a5e7982fddb457cc8887014ed11604eae9a7980","tid":808294,"uid":78143,"like":145,"dislike":3,"score":142,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/211704_2db93d9dad696f25d13262cfa8b165dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F211704_2db93d9dad696f25d13262cfa8b165dc.jpg&h=cc048367&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"739c2b8ccb4032c71d778bbcb0acae6412e52d9d","tid":808294,"uid":6604,"like":114,"dislike":2,"score":112,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"咁市民覺得冇問題<br />\n但你覺得有問題<br />\n咁係湯渣華你自己嘅問題<br />\n有問題就去睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"a75cf8ff3e24eafdcde3450fa968ca46fd50d321","tid":808294,"uid":152476,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"唔係支共隻狗點會覺得有問題"},{"pid":"6aa16644f4903d46785d195a006d9f49cdf7d780","tid":808294,"uid":187957,"like"